    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hexo是一个基于nodejs的静态博客网站生成器，先在本地搭建再部署到github/gitee。</p><hr><p>系统：win10</p><h3 id="一、本地安装"><a href="#一、本地安装" class="headerlink" title="一、本地安装"></a>一、本地安装</h3><ul><li><p>安装node.js（官网自行下载）</p></li><li><p>安装淘宝的cnpm管理器</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry&#x3D;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>安装hexo框架</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>创建blog目录</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>进入blog目录</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>官网下载git并配置坏境</li></ul><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/06/01/UGYXk6L39mfSMPZ.png" alt="坏境变量"></p><ul><li>打开Git CMD，输入hexo init  生成博客、初始化博客。</li></ul><h3 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/06/01/3fso2chYBeVTGuz.png" alt="hello init"></h3><ul><li><p>本地访问地址—<a href="http://localhost:4000/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000/</a></p></li><li><p>创建新文章</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n &quot;XXX&quot;   #XXX为文章标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>清理缓存，重新生成</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="二、远端部署"><a href="#二、远端部署" class="headerlink" title="二、远端部署"></a>二、远端部署</h3><ul><li><p>首先注册一个github账号</p></li><li><p>创建一个新的仓库（名字一定和自己的Github账号相同）</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/06/01/wU178l93VyfzHWi.jpg" alt="create repo"></p><ul><li>在blog目录下安装git部署插件</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>修改_config.yml文件内容</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">type: git</span><br><span class="line">repo: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;YourGithubName&#x2F;YourGithubName.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>部署到Github仓库</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>查看博客</li></ul><p><a href="https://YourGithubName.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://YourGithubName.github.io/</a></p><h3 id="三、更换主题（以yilia主题为例）"><a href="#三、更换主题（以yilia主题为例）" class="headerlink" title="三、更换主题（以yilia主题为例）"></a>三、更换主题（以yilia主题为例）</h3><ul><li>修改hexo根目录下的 _config.yml 文件 </li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: yilia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="四、小结"><a href="#四、小结" class="headerlink" title="四、小结"></a>四、小结</h3><ul><li>清缓存</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>生成</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>部署远端</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>查看</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;YourGithubName.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>ps：若觉得github访问太慢，可部署到gitee上，方法同理。</p>]]></content>
    
